eadPara></HandL><TailParas fid="td"><Para>Should MOE not provide more details on its new computerised balloting system for Primary 1 registration? How does the system work? What are the factors that are taken into account?</Para><Para>The balloting process to fill Primary 1 vacancies should not only be transparent and fair, but must also be seen to be so.</Para><Para>Tan Soon Hock</Para></TailParas><Byline fid="by" index="field"></Byline><Credit fid="cr" index="field"></Credit><Contact fid="ct" index="field"></Contact><Notes fid="rf" index="field"></Notes><Art fid="art" index="field"></Art><Copyright fid="cy" index="field">(c) 2018 Singapore Press Holdings Limited </Copyright></Article></ArchiveDoc><AdocTOC adoctype="article"><Item size="0" ref="distdoc:archive/ArchiveDoc::Article" type="arttext"></Item><Item size="0" ref="distdoc:archive/InvertText" type="invtext"></Item></AdocTOC></DistDoc>

